  "3093870": {
    "name": "One Long Night with the Circleheads",
    "steam_appid": 3093870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093870/extras/94c5a7a31be4d0f63decf801f35c2149.webp?t=1768631791\" width=558 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as 9-year-old Barney Bubbs, a runaway orphan forced to seek shelter in a  shed during a nasty thunderstorm. In doing so, Barney unexpectedly finds himself trapped in a pocket dimension called the &quot;Fun Depot&quot; with quirky sphere-headed beings. Thankfully, though, Barney has nothing to worry about! After all, these Circleheads just want to have <strong><i>FUNFUNFUNFUNFUNFUNFUNFUNFUNFUNFUNFUN!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>THIS GAME CONTAINS FLASHING LIGHTS, DISTURBING IMAGERY, AND LOUD NOISES!</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are forced to spend one long night  in the Fun Depot with the Circleheads. Look on your tablet to keep tabs on them as well as the many childhood-come-to-life rooms that they inhabit. Use your lasers and lights to check outside your room and keep any unwanted pests out. Make the call: trust the Circleheads, or think twice? Either way, you’ll be in for a FUNFUNFUNFUN time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your experience at the Fun Depot you’ll become well acquainted with the Circleheads: Greg (the giggly leader), Benjy (the bigoted weirdo), Carol (the alcoholic sweetheart), Fabio (the hermit clown), and Henry (the narcoleptic handyman). Are they on the level, or is there more to them than meets the eye…?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONTROLS:</strong> As long as you’ve got a functioning mouse and keyboard, you’re golden! <strong>Keep your middle mouse button handy! </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093870/extras/9d794cea9264bce88ba583f44bd76961.poster.avif?t=1768631791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093870/extras/9d794cea9264bce88ba583f44bd76961.webm?t=1768631791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093870/extras/9d794cea9264bce88ba583f44bd76961.mp4?t=1768631791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A point-and-click survival horror game made with Clickteam Fusion 2.5. My first ever completed game! Heavily inspired by Scott Cawthon.</i></p>",
